Package org.planit.network.macroscopic.physical

Class MacroscopicLinkSegmentTypeImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.planit.network.macroscopic.physical.MacroscopicLinkSegmentTypeImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable, Comparable<Idable>, ExternalIdable, Idable, MacroscopicLinkSegmentType
    public class MacroscopicLinkSegmentTypeImpl
extends Object
implements MacroscopicLinkSegmentType
    Each macroscopic link segment is of a particular type reflecting segment specific properties. On top of the segment specific properties each segment can have user class specific properties as well.
    Author:
    markr
